They bribe their special interests with massive subsidies -solar, wind, teachers unions, you name it. And then they tell you it’s for your own good. They tell you to forget about inflation or the debt your kids will owe. You don’t believe them, so they add more spending to the bill and tell you it’s for you. node.text: For about 48 hours the Energy and Commerce Committee is debating sections of the absurd $3.5T spending bill. If there’s one thing to remember about this bill, it is this: their spending is nothing but bribery. They bribe their special interests with massive subsidies -solar, wind, teachers unions, you name it. And then they tell you it’s for your own good. They tell you to forget about inflation or the debt your kids will owe. You don’t believe them, so they add more spending to the bill and tell you it’s for you. They try and bribe YOU into voting for them. And they’re bribing you with your own money and your children’s debt.
